---
title: Mild Thai Coconut Chicken with Asian Greens & Garlic Rice
description: With tender chicken, colourful veggies and an infusion of ginger and garlic, this coconut sauce is mild enough for picky eaters but
has a deep flavour that will still keep the grown-ups satisfied.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/coconut-chicken-oyster-sauce-curry-ed746643.jpg
